      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点和终点都用[*]表示。那第一个状态是\"Proposed\"吗？谁来触发从Proposed到Approved的转移？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
